          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The For The People Act, or H.R. 1, the democracy reform bill that passed the House of Representatives last week, would prevent lawmakers from sitting on the boards of for-profit corporations. According to an analysis by ",
